# waddle_controller (`apps/waddle_controller`)

- **SOLID**: keep API clients (`src/api/`), persistence (`src/storage/`), server logic (`server/src/`), and pure helpers (`src/util/`, `src/auth/`) free of React; pages compose those modules. Do not embed fetch or `localStorage`/`sessionStorage` directly in page components when a storage or API helper already exists.
- **BFF**: optional Hono server in `server/`; SPA calls `/bff/v1/*` via `bffClient` with `credentials: 'include'`. Never store plaintext passwords in SQLite (Argon2 hashes only).
- **TDD**: add or extend a failing Vitest test (`src/**/*.test.ts`) before production changes in gated paths (`auth/`, `api/`, `storage/`, `util/*.ts`, `constants/`).
- **Coverage**: CI enforces **≥ 80%** line coverage on gated logic via [`tool/coverage_check.mjs`](../../apps/waddle_controller/tool/coverage_check.mjs); **90%** is the aspirational target (warn only). UI shells (`pages/`, `layout/`, `components/`, `context/`, `App.tsx`, `main.tsx`) are outside the floor until covered with React Testing Library.
- **Pre-commit**: from `apps/waddle_controller`, run `npm run lint` (zero issues), `npm run test:coverage`, `npm run coverage:check`, and `npm run build`.
- **Secrets**: never commit display API keys or session tokens; display sessions (API key + adopted role) live in `localStorage` per display id; when controller auth is enabled, keys are also encrypted in SQLite `user_displays`. Display base URLs in `localStorage` only. All display REST uses `/bff/v1/proxy/*`.
- **Role permissions**: keep [`src/auth/rolePermissions.ts`](../../apps/waddle_controller/src/auth/rolePermissions.ts) in sync with `packages/waddle_shared/lib/auth/role_permissions.dart`.
- **Docs**: update [`apps/waddle_controller/README.md`](../../apps/waddle_controller/README.md) when operator workflows or env/proxy setup change.

See [`waddle-controller-tests.mdc`](waddle-controller-tests.mdc) for test-file conventions.
